title: Day 8: The Caldwell, Schoenefeld and Lillis Tricycle
description:
Gold-medalist skiers Ashley Caldwell, Justin Schoenefeld and Christopher Lillis join In the Village to discuss their love tricycle, pre-competition nerves and not knowing they were underdogs. 

Follow In The Village on Apple Podcasts for an inside look at the athlete life in Beijing, and watch all the Olympic action unfold on the networks of NBC
author: tess.quinlan@nbcuni.com (NBC Olympics)
